Unorg. Fed. Terr. (1861-03-02)

1861/03/02 -> 1890/05/01

The United States created Dakota Territory from Nebraska Territory and Unorganized Federal Territory.

(Dak. Terr. Laws 1862, 1st sess., pp. 21-28; U.S. Stat., vol. 12, ch. 86[1861]/pp. 239-244; Van Zandt, 134, 136-137)
